title: Fearless - Jet Li
description: Jet Li&#039;s final movie in which he will be the main character. The movie is about Huo Yin Jia (Master YinJia) and his quest to become powerful. Striving to become the number 1 fighter in all of Tiensen, YinJia loses touch with his roots, loses friends, family, and becomes nothing but a shell of a man, good for nothing more than fighting. The real struggle begins when he must fight not for glory, but to retake everything he lost because of his ignorange in the past.
